{"tid":2333209,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"封黎智英年度人物 彭定康讚為港奮戰 「中共拘民主派人士 只會為抗爭添光環」","createTime":"2020-12-20T08:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T08:37:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df614fc1bf1bdded146cebac0dde0e848ce53fe7","tid":2333209,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T08:19:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201220/PDO56N7NHNARFOUBCDYFYIXHME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201220%2FPDO56N7NHNARFOUBCDYFYIXHME%2F&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIa0GH2IkZjUVJy%2ByuJI4obM%3D&h=65511c51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201220%2FPDO56N7NHNARFOUBCDYFYIXHME%2F&h=85819f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201220/PDO56N7NHNARFOUBCDYFYIXHME/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n封黎智英年度人物 彭定康讚為港奮戰<br />\n「中共拘民主派人士 只會為抗爭添光環」<br />\n<br />\n【國際關注】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：WSJ：中共大抓捕旨在測試拜登<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】壹傳媒創辦人黎智英。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康在文章中表示，中國政府討厭黎智英的原因，是黎智英對自由有熱情，「他的手銬和鎖鏈，正正悲哀地象徵曾經自由的香港，在2020年發生甚麼事」。<br />\n<br />\n他稱黎智英是港版國安法下最新及最知名的受害者，他12歲從中國大陸偷渡到香港後白手興家，但一直沒有忘記給予他財富的自由和法治價值，1989年六四事件後，黎智英公開批評時任中國國務院總理李鵬，導致黎智英當時擁有的時裝企業佐丹奴遭中共打壓。彭定康進而提到黎智英後來創立《壹週刊》及《蘋果日報》，一直支持民主價值，形容黎智英視香港為家，有決心為他所愛的城市奮戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/b_62R3PkiWoLqBjBco8a0E2-csQ=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ELBSLFTJSVERLEPFHWWWPSUBYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fb_62R3PkiWoLqBjBco8a0E2-csQ%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FELBSLFTJSVERLEPFHWWWPSUBYY.jpg&h=b8fd9f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前港督彭定康指中共打壓香港民主派，只會適得其反。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n批評中共令世人受害<br />\n<br />\n彭定康指，黎智英面臨的控罪是針對他的原則和勇氣，還有對信念的堅持不屈，批評中共與少數香港的奉承者針對式報復黎智英，形容他們將永遠留下惡名，但即使黎智英入獄，亦只會為民主抗爭的人增添光環，吸納更多支持，「想想馬丁路德金、曼德拉、哈維爾，現在想想黎智英，我心目中的年度人物」。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康形容，中國國家主席習近平是全球對民主價值威脅最嚴重的人，稱中共「一整年都使世人受害」，指摘中共在武漢肺炎爆發初期隱瞞疫情，更把勇於揭發疫情的醫生滅聲，這些事件警醒世界「我們將要面對甚麼將來」。不僅如此，中國亦與印度在邊境爆發衝突，據報曾殺害印度士兵，還在國際水域威嚇其他國家的漁船，並持續威脅台灣，又持續在新疆針對維吾爾人，以及打擊香港自由。<br />\n<br />\n他指，中國顯然恐懼選舉及遊行示威，因為這反映大多數香港人像台灣一樣，拒絕擁抱「愛國就必須愛中共」的論述，但香港至少三分二居民都是逃避中共的人及其後代，他們只想保留過往讓香港得以繁榮並成為國際經濟中心的制度，即三權分立、言論自由及市場經濟等。然而這些開放社會的價值，卻令習近平的政權感到恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n近期中國與多個西方國家出現糾紛，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7lzIlfvlRyE6SXsxko4O7bAwcJw=/1994x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ODL3PGUZHBBOZALXNMUENPZVXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7lzIlfvlRyE6SXsxko4O7bAwcJw%3D%2F1994x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FODL3PGUZHBBOZALXNMUENPZVXQ.jpg&h=16b4429c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■彭定康將黎智英封為其心目中的年度人物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dKjmJvN-3UHqQQwupsBwt9TEZjQ=/1628x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IZNHU5BIKVAHXCVXKNSU4N2EKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdKjmJvN-3UHqQQwupsBwt9TEZjQ%3D%2F1628x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIZNHU5BIKVAHXCVXKNSU4N2EKM.jpg&h=ca78fa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英被港府以港版國安法起訴，未審先拘押在赤柱監獄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲：激起反中情緒<br />\n<br />\n台北市長柯文哲同樣聲援黎智英，指他身為大老闆，「本可帶着錢遠走海外，舒服過日子」，但他選擇留在香港繼續堅持他的理念、表達其想法，故覺得他很有氣魄，代表他是一個很有個性、很有想法的人。柯文哲又指看到黎被捕、被警方鎖上鐵鏈手銬的照片，只會激起台灣更大的反中情緒。新北市長侯友宜昨日亦表示，黎智英捍衞的是民主與新聞自由的普世價值。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EUxr_9zYDP7nQLArAaA-xtMnlZc=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UDOWFAJXAZF55HTXTE6HB4F5AI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEUxr_9zYDP7nQLArAaA-xtMnlZc%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUDOWFAJXAZF55HTXTE6HB4F5AI.jpg&h=c75072a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■台北市長柯文哲讚揚黎智英留守香港堅持理念很有氣魄。"},{"pid":"6a306cd3cba8dfc6654de6756692251eba8eb176","tid":2333209,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T08:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b9ad68c3d2b1c3cedf5d9b6ed1383704b9f262","tid":2333209,"uid":69334,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T08:25:04.000Z","msg":"光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁制裁得未"},{"pid":"53fd04b9cb8ea25782e2e14953eae1964fceba99","tid":2333209,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76b9ad68c3d2b1c3cedf5d9b6ed1383704b9f262","tid":2333209,"uid":69334,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T08:25:04.000Z","msg":"光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁制裁得未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"英國幾時先做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}